{"tid":1648831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10.1 遍地開花 成功嗎？成功！但是講賀佢老母講左幾耐？耐左幾個月啊！","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T12:36:03.000Z","uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0edc57c84fffdac64096a2183b2e28b33f767a","tid":1648831,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"遍地開花已經討論過演變成7大戰區,<br />\n點解成班連登軍師會去返18區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時開始宣傳遍地開花？琴日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講聽日真是唔知你地班人想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十八區各個商場集結？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌你老母當初就是講緊分太多區會唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班連登仔人地宣傳去港島ThankyouWorld, 個搞手擺烏龍, 宣傳曬先出曬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好啦 班軍師就嫌棄個摺紙左膠唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1011臨急臨忙話要搞十八區開花, 用埋個張商場做集合地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1011晚伏左幾個手足無人出去, 到1013話搞開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申支持 但是成班垃圾軍師傳埋個張18區商場集合點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 101遍地開花都是要幾個區集合埋一齊, 再遊擊快閃, 班狗出嚟 就打 或者 彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話叫人去遊行就送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔是為屌而屌！<br />\n提議：10.1模式 7大戰區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初頭以各區遊行聚人和理非出力, 當然唔排除聽日沒人去開花就屌曬鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今個星期六日亂到7彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望民陣盡快宣佈10.20遊行重整旗鼓啦<br />\n<br />\n我話比聽點解文宣圖亂到7彩？唔是因為一日得一個活動 而是你地堅持遍地開花 活動都遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屌你老母你知唔知好多活動和理非唔介意山長水遠搵路去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而你地自己區嘅人真是全部出曬去支持？<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦 遍地開花要成功, 基礎人數要非常巨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一日吹雞遊行 今日見到頂多數千人逾萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 聽日去摺紙 摺摺下要行下街做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5562d3584b96b0b06bb3b6cb60adf0be1cd16815","tid":1648831,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"d697cfd99b6d2792b6ee2a9b5e68fdffa99aec3e","tid":1648831,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"裝修18區開花 戰役5區革命<br />\n<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"5cbb75e8e3350138b18d3061bfbd2261b875e6cb","tid":1648831,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5562d3584b96b0b06bb3b6cb60adf0be1cd16815","tid":1648831,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"得 留名Cap圖<br />\n<br />\n聽日 我都希望香港人夠團結 一日前連登話遍地開花就真是開花到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f555aca5740101b568400f6341cccb1949fb215a","tid":1648831,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d697cfd99b6d2792b6ee2a9b5e68fdffa99aec3e","tid":1648831,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"裝修18區開花 戰役5區革命<br />\n<br />\n支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"根本就應該5~7區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4df8977dcd151cc19b757915c578cd6042bdb9c","tid":1648831,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f555aca5740101b56